PAUL L off slow, stalked pace along the inside on the backstretch, continued to save ground on the turn and failed to improve. ONE LITTLE INDIAN off slow and trailed well off the rail on the backstretch, continued off the rail on the turn, and failed to improve in the lane. SMUGGLER'S COVE quickly fell back on the backstretch, kept off the rail, went to inside into the turn and fail to threaten.

HOLYJAZZ vied for lead two wide on the backstretch, continued two wide on the turn, and weakened early in upper stretch.
